{"tid":212630,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車仔定熱刺?","createTime":"2017-04-22T15:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T02:28:53.000Z","uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67609d881da97c5afb1a12e3705d58bfb929b4dc","tid":212630,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"原本睇到車仔季中領先十幾分, 仲以為車仔拎硬英超<br />\n點知突然輸左兩場, 而家只領先4分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (對曼聯真心肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n足總盃冇嫁啦, 咁嘅士氣贏唔到熱刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過英超就唔知啦, 畢業生熱刺嘅賽程比車仔難打<br />\n作為車迷我當然支持我車<br />\n不過干地嘅戰術似乎開始比人破到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢一定要諗下新變招 (試下Ake, 亞依, 查路巴正選都好, 尤其而家哥斯達嘅表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n如果唔係真係隨時比熱刺反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為個人認為熱刺都幾有機會贏晒獌妓兩隊 (妓嘅近期表現真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"c93bbe3f95ed08eccd605f3931e632ad45809ad2","tid":212630,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"北倫敦打比個陣就會唔同"},{"pid":"1d074b4667922844bb8c863415489c05ada57f59","tid":212630,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"車今年如果冇雙冠，其實幾難睇"},{"pid":"f1f480e05bf0e758a6c0cc5deb5680eabfa38fe7","tid":212630,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>車今年如果冇雙冠，其實幾難睇</blockquote><br />\n有幾難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難睇得過上年降班區"},{"pid":"46cfb4a8e1bc8a2ffb5048f970d66d79a0a975bc","tid":212630,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"撐車啦"},{"pid":"0a43075de2da8a0eece36a4ac227ce8d0a9e1a0c","tid":212630,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1851d0fa714e43fa1f73c3ecafa8ab22064cf747","tid":212630,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20695f5517314fe3f82d95805eef0dc4189c0841","tid":212630,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>車今年如果冇雙冠，其實幾難睇</blockquote><br />\n有幾難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難睇得過上年降班區</blockquote><br />\n英超唔7理論上都冇問題既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聯賽車都穩嘅，足總盃賽一場過就熱佔優<br />\n<br />\n上年車都歐聯16強，今年只專注本土三項比賽，以車嘅班底，要贏其中兩個唔過份，而家兩條戰線俾熱搞到有暗湧，幾牙煙下<br />\n<br />\n題外話，曼有機做另類三冠王，歐覇+聯賽盃+社區盾+歐聯資格，就咁睇結果，車就算雙冠都未必夠曼威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bbef1c8d098a64de6781253f4d34b35c3d32ec","tid":212630,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撐車啦</blockquote><br />\n我係車迷都覺得熱刺人腳好J<br />\n後生又有表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n卡尼, 阿里, 艾歷臣 (fifa好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 路斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e5bd1132924473b6688e77b4ead6e6581e45d4","tid":212630,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>車今年如果冇雙冠，其實幾難睇</blockquote><br />\n有幾難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難睇得過上年降班區</blockquote><br />\n英超唔7理論上都冇問題既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聯賽車都穩嘅，足總盃賽一場過就熱佔優</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eeb026a48bbda843c025f1ef015df70c5305e7","tid":212630,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T02:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>車今年如果冇雙冠，其實幾難睇</blockquote><br />\n有幾難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難睇得過上年降班區</blockquote><br />\n英超唔7理論上都冇問題既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聯賽車都穩嘅，足總盃賽一場過就熱佔優</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都估唔到我車會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有馬迪一腳靚遠射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}